## Step 3 — Use the passed dates in `DemandHandlerImpl`, remove per-item computation

```java
@Override
public List<JSONObject> generateOutputResult(OnDemandScopeDetailsDto item) {
    List<JSONObject> outputList = new ArrayList<>();
    try {
        ResolvedRequestParamsContext params = resolveRequestParams(item);
        RequestDatesContext dates = resolveDates(item);   // now reads today/yesterday from item

        String onDemandFileName = dates.isHistorical() && !params.onDemandFileName().isEmpty()
                ? toHistoricalFileName(params.onDemandFileName(), dates.today())
                : params.onDemandFileName();

        JsonNode rootNode = MAPPER.readTree(String.valueOf(item.getHeaderParams().get(FACTSET)));
        Set<String> processedIdentifiers = new HashSet<>();

        for (String identifier : params.identifiers()) {
            String identifierStr = resolveIdentifierValue(item, identifier);
            if (identifierStr == null || !processedIdentifiers.add(identifierStr)) {
                continue;
            }
            JSONObject output = new JSONObject();
            populateResultForIdentifier(item, output, rootNode, identifier, params, dates, onDemandFileName);
            outputList.add(output);
        }
    } catch (Exception e) {
        log.error("Error in OnDemand request file format for {}", item.getProviderName(), e);
    }
    return outputList;
}

/**
 * Reads the job-level today/yesterday (computed once upstream) and resolves the
 * request date for this item. Historical items use the historical date; others
 * use yesterday.
 */
private RequestDatesContext resolveDates(OnDemandScopeDetailsDto item) {
    String historicalDate = Objects.toString(item.getItem().get(HISTORICAL_DATE), "").trim();
    boolean isHistorical = !historicalDate.isBlank();

    String today = item.getToday();
    String yesterday = item.getYesterday();
    String requestDate = isHistorical ? historicalDate : yesterday;

    return new RequestDatesContext(isHistorical, isHistorical ? historicalDate : null,
            today, requestDate);
}
```

