## Why this satisfies Imen's comment

- **Computed once** — `LocalDate.now()` called a single time in `getVacationDetails`, not per item ✅
- **Midnight-safe** — all items in one job run share the exact same `today`/`yesterday` snapshot ✅
- **Passed down** — via the DTO, the natural carrier already flowing into `generateOutputResult` ✅

